data.description: Welcome to this charming, single-story, 3-bed, 2-bath home on a spacious corner lot. While HOA fees are LOW, Spanish Oaks is a well-kept community nestled amidst mature oak trees. With its bright and well-kept interior, this home is ready for a new owner in any stage of life. The primary bedroom is filled with light, complemented by an en-suite bath and a large walk-in-closet. A jack-and-jill bath conjoins two additional bedrooms that could be used as an office or hobby room, as well. Outside, the screened-in patio and large lot provide plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the beauty of the surrounding nature. Conveniently located near shopping and island amenities, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and lifestyle.
